thread.title: Paul Vidilini
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Paul Vidilini

author: Paul Vidilini
title: Paul Vidilini
text: I found them online and was a bit wary about the prospect of online purchase. I should not have worried as the service was tops and the price was great. I was very impressed with the whole transaction from go to whoa. I have told others about them and will use them for all future purchases.
